<![endif]-->  <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>I heard there's an HBO series for the Game of Thrones books<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>Not that I've read them, but I've always enjoyed film fantasy more than print.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>When 10 pages of scene description can be represented in a single shot.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Or 10 pages of Bible-esque backstory can be omitted.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>&quot;And Etheres begot Indular who was brother if Ozishoot...&quot;<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b><em>Who is the guy, why is he fighting demons? What drives him? What are his fears? That's what I need to know.</em><br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>&quot;And in the 127th year of the second age, Lensilar of Celexia ascended the throne of Midlothian...&quot;<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>And there was much rejoicing.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>&quot;And it was the wedding of Bulthelicks IX to her 1/4 brother Timildon II...&quot;<br /><b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>ahahaha<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Figure that out!<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>What kind of genetics are going on in this world?<br /><b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>They're quad-gendered!<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>It takes three dicks into one front hole to make a baby<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>ew.<span style="">&nbsp; </span>also crowded.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Not all at once<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>ah.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>I think four genders is more interesting<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Yeah, we're too square thinking dicks and front holes.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>There's one &quot;female&quot; and three &quot;others&quot;<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>They all have some part to play<br /><b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>A fucks B and produces some sort of blastocyst which B then ... ejaculates into C, and C's body does something else to it, adding more genetic material, then finally C fucks D, who has the womb.<span style="">&nbsp; </span>And the tits.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>JESUS<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Yeah, everyone gets into it<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>It'd have to happen quickly though<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>Otherwise there's too much logistics. It'd be impossible to have babies after one drunken night, and what fun would that be?<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Nah<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Check it out..<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>A fires off many things that seed themselves in B<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>Ah... and those things can &quot;live&quot; in B for a while.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Right. A dozen or so take hold in B and then B fires them off into C<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>It's a species that lives like 1000 years<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>So having kids has to be rare<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>What would their anatomy be like?<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>Two of the genders will need both inputs and outputs.<br /><b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">Rupert: </span></b>Here's something to think about, does A ever fuck D? What about A and C? B and D?<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>Well, B, C, and D all need moist holes.<span style="">&nbsp; </span>A, B, and C all need things to stick in them.<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>Not only would churches decide homosexuality to be a sin, but it'd be a sin for A to fuck C or D, etc...<br /> <b><span style="color: rgb(32, 74, 135);">Me: </span></b>Religions would have all kinds of guilt to play on.</p>
